============================================================================
ASP.NET MVC 3 Gravatar Html Helper
============================================================================

Requirements: .NET Framework 4.0, ASP.NET MVC 3 Framework

============================================================================
Instructions:
============================================================================
Compile project as standalone or add project to your solution.
Add a reference to the Assembly in your MVC 3 project

============================================================================
Usage:
============================================================================
Using the Razoe View Engine:
@Html.GetGravatarTag(email, size, link, rating, alt, title, cssClass)

============================================================================
Parameters:
============================================================================
email - The email address of the user you want to retrieve the gravatar for
This address will not be exposed to the page

size - The size of the image to display

link - Where you want to image to link to

rating - Defaults to PG, change if you don't mind

alt/title - The alt and title tags of the image

cssClass - The css class you want applied to the image

==========================================================================
Future Improvements:
==========================================================================
Quick Gravatar - Create gravatar by only passing in email address

